<p>&#8216;The Law Commission of England and Wales has set out its recommendations to reform weddings law, proposing a fairer system that it says will give couples more choice over where and how their wedding takes place.&#8217;</p>
<p><a href="https://www.localgovernmentlawyer.co.uk/governance/396-governance-news/51095-law-commission-unveils-plans-for-reforms-to-confusing-out-of-date-and-restrictive-weddings-law">Full Story</a></p><p>Local Government Lawyer, 19th July 2022</p><p>Source: <a href="https://www.localgovernmentlawyer.co.uk">www.localgovernmentlawyer.co.uk</a></p>